# CoffeeGrams — repository ignore rules
# Covers Swift Package Manager, Xcode, and macOS artifacts.

## macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Icon?

## Swift Package Manager
.build/
.swiftpm/
Package.resolved      # keep out for an app; re-add if you want pinned deps committed

## Xcode (app target, added in M5+)
DerivedData/
build/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint
xcuserdata/
*.moved-aside
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.dSYM.zip
*.dSYM

## Xcode project user-specific files (keep the shared .xcodeproj/.xcworkspace)
*.xcodeproj/project.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/
*.xcodeproj/xcuserdata/
*.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/

## Secrets / signing — never commit these
*.p12
*.mobileprovision
*.cer
AuthKey_*.p8
.env
secrets.xcconfig
